Copyright.RotationInfo: The channels for this survey were collected at various azimuths, but ROTSPEC says 0. For archiving we infer that everything has been rotated to geographic, and no further rotation is required. Full error covariances allow for arbitrary rotations in the future.
Copyright.AdditionalInfo: These data were converted from the original EDI SPECTRA format using EMTF FCU 4.0 developed by Anna Kelbert, USGS last updated in Nov 2017. This novel algorithm allows for estimation of full error covariances from cross-power spectra. We thank Xavier Garcia and Gary Egbert for valuable advice that helped develop the spectra conversion algorithm.
